Box__tD7YI contentBox mb-last-0 InfoBox_infoBox__VUOVC infoBox py-8 p-5 p-xl-16 px-xxl-12 pb-xxl-12 mb-last-0 h-100 undefined bg-grey-dark text-white Box_box--rounded-lg__uS5ZG"><h3 class="mb-5 mb-xl-6"><span>Když chcete pronájem bez provize...</span></h3><p class="InfoBox_infoBoxText__abyTE mt-auto text-perex"><span>S realitní kanceláří platíte provizi i v případě nájmu. Obvyklá provize je rovna jednomu mesíčnímu nájmu, často 15 - 20 000 Kč.</span></p></div></div></div></section><section class="box Section_section__gjwvr section"><div class="PromoBox_promoBox__CYQj_"><div class="box ContentBox_contentBox__tD7YI contentBox mb-last-0 PromoBox_promoBoxContent__mucT1 py-8 px-5 p-xl-15 pt-xl-20 mb-last-0 bg-grey-light Box_box--rounded-xl___MO4i"><div class="h-100 vstack"><h2 class="PromoBox_promoBoxHeading__BymA1 mb-7 mb-md-10 mb-lg-18 text-title"><span>Nabídněte svou nemovitost <br/> ostatním</span></h2><p class="mb-7 mb-md-10 text-perex"><span>Ať už chcete prodat nebo pronajmout, s námi máte na výběr. Můžete to zkusit sami nebo vám s tím pomůžeme.</span></p><div class="box mt-auto align-self-md-start"><a class="btn btn-secondary w-100 btn-side-to-side" href="https://www.bezrealitky.cz/pro-majitele"><span class="text-cta"><span>Nabídnout nemovitost</span></span><span class="Icon_icon__ZG9ss icon Icon_icon--end__MNPcU"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none"><path d="M10.25 2.25a3.5 3.5 0 013.475 3.08c.74.088 1.458.397 2.05.925l.154.147 4.513 4.513a4.465 4.465 0 01.159 6.148l-.159.166-.22.221a4.465 4.465 0 01-6.149.159l-.166-.159-2.988-2.986c-.15.129-.309.25-.474.362l-.196.126v4.055a1.748 1.748 0 01-.397 1.103l-.116.127-1.002 1.003a1.747 1.747 0 01-2.345.111l-.125-.113-1.002-1.005a1.748 1.748 0 01-.503-1.063l-.009-.172.002-4.045-.195-.126a5.223 5.223 0 01-2.302-4.087l-.005-.24a5.252 5.252 0 014.53-5.2 3.5 3.5 0 013.47-3.05zm-6.5 8.25a3.73 3.73 0 001.9 3.242l.23.122.08.053.073.064.063.072.054.08.043.086.032.093.02.09